    "description": "## Description\n\nAzure Advisor detected that the following **App Service Plan** may be an **unused / empty plan** and could potentially be deleted to reduce cost.  \nThis workflow uses **Azure Advisor** as the source of detection.\n\n## How It Works\n\n- Query **Azure Advisor recommendations** across selected subscriptions.  \n\n- Filter recommendations to those related to **App Service Plans** (`Microsoft.Web/serverFarms`).  \n\n- For each matching recommendation:  \n  1. Read the related **resource ID** from Advisor output.  \n  2. Resolve the actual Azure resource to get its **region**.  \n  3. Compare the resolved region against the selected workflow regions.  \n  4. Query cost data for that specific resource using **Azure Cost Management Query API**.  \n  5. If the recommendation matches the selected scope, add it as an **Opportunity** with estimated savings based on observed cost data.\n\n## Required Azure Permissions\n\n- `Microsoft.Advisor/recommendations/read`  \n- `Microsoft.Web/serverfarms/read`  \n- `Microsoft.Resources/subscriptions/resourceGroups/read`  \n- `Microsoft.Resources/subscriptions/resources/read`  \n- `Microsoft.CostManagement/query/read`  "
  },
